<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px;">
      <h1 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 20px;">Email Verification</h1>

      <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

      <p>Thank you for signing up! Please use the following verification code to verify your email address:</p>

      <div style="background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 36px; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #3498db; margin: 0; font-family: monospace;">{{verificationCode}}</h2>
      </div>

      <p><strong>This code will expire in {{expiresIn}} minutes.</strong></p>

      <p>If you didn't request this verification, please ignore this email.</p>

      <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 30px 0;">

      <p style="color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 14px;">
        This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
